name: Dominique Tipper
description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Dominique Tipper is a British actress, dancer and singer mostly known for her role as Naomi Nagata in the TV sci-fi show The Expanse.

It's a 900-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (dt1pper:0.99), a woman, RAW, close portrait photo, long brown coat, (turtleneck sweater:1.2), trousers, slim body, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3 sharp focus, f 5.6"
